Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.55,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're here earlier than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:24.95,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.32,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:30.26,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry, but don't talk to me until we stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.99,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs26\b0\c&HBFBFBF&}Note: The symbol on the rear windscreen represents a driver who just acquired the license.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:45.23,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yusuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.24,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too far. Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.01,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, we're finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:04.08,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun, good job. You're sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:08.65,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.93,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Orisaku-san and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:24.21,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I meant Akira and I are newlyweds as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:30.32,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We had many obstacles, but we're finally starting a new and exciting life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:31.68,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.49,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is our treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.23,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.33,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, you are my most valuable treasure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.67,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.64,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, would you like to take a bath first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.74,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:05.81,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.36,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is our first night together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:26.33,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting in bed feels awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.21,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling a bit shy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:31.47,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Soon... I am nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:36.88,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:40.18,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a lot of work so I couldn't wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.28,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.55,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to spend the rest of our lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.72,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.29,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, good job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.93,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well... you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.73,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must be tired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.26,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was hoping we would... but can't blame her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.00,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun, are you already sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.64,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I, I meant no, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.51,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, but also very nervous and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm finally your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:21.68,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And when I think you're finally my husband, my sleepiness went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.92,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Orisaku-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you called me Orisaku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.75,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm now Oshima Akira so call me Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.16,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.00,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.69,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.47,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.08,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.22,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.80,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.26,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:36.46,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're grownups... it's fine, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.13,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is Akira's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.46,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.63,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.37,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time, gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.35,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.91,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold it in, so continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.22,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.12,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.18,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.00,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.49,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.16,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.36,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.97,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So cute...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.77,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stick it in... OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.25,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.52,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun... we have to make yours wet too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.48,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.95,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's starting to feel good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.54,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:40.91,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were tired, Yusuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.92,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, there's always tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:48.65,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If not, there's always the day after so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.92,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Day after tomorrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:55.49,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up Yusuke-kun, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.50,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.08,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.85,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.45,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.96,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yusuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.46,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready, let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.69,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go to the studio today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.29,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I can't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.63,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I better dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:36.50,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This came out of the boxes, but who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:43.74,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's an old friend of mine who is a few years younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:52.18,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was very sick and had to move to America for treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.42,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I haven't seen her ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.85,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I kept this picture as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:04.13,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see, well I'm not worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.86,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.40,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! And hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:19.18,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yusuke-kun, we're going to get married one day.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.14,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright, Akko, I promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.95,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.75,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.45,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun, lets do our best tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.42,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.24,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.41,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a housewife as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.01,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.46,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams have come true, going to work on a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.07,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yusuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.87,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:29.18,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This person saw my 8mm movie and liked my work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.62,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He even offered me a job here. He is the Vice President, Fujimiya Shizuma-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.59,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy, Shizuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.59,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not going to go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.96,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how is that white house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:51.57,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, thank you for letting us know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.70,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how is your sex life with Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.54,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.35,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What to cook tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.55,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something with meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:11.55,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, today we have a big sale on steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.82,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you? I mean that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.86,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.96,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:24.70,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I usually get housewives here so I sense these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.14,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.68,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, movie directors are so demanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.77,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't bring the actress, I'll get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.05,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.45,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry to the studi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.46,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.30,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.87,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky to see the naked body of an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.82,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.28,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:14.95,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.79,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.42,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.55,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start now, so please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.20,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.63,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Better be more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.50,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, she had a great body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.77,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.58,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you guys later, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.49,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.43,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-san, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing me here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.49,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:06.43,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.30,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.99,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're Yusuke-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.87,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What does she want...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.27,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I better hurry home to Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.31,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.02,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.71,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to have dinner first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.15,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:58.32,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:02.79,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Orisaku... no, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.36,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best coordinating for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:09.27,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what would you like to have first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.10,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.91,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.04,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.12,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Yusuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.72,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yusuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.64,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.26,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:11.80,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.90,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Assistant Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.70,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here, Misaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.70,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:27.78,Tsuma_main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're friends with the actress Misaki Atsuko-san?
